 Galvatron looked at her. He didnt say anythign but i think she took what he 
said the wrong way. he was very impressed by her. he hoped she would stay. 
"Yes that would be it. They may still be there. If your planning to stay 
those quarters can be your for as long as you want." He typed in some numbers 
and the feactions names came up over all the bases. His was not on there for 
while cloaked it wasnt detectable on any scanner. he pointed on the map. 
"This is where we are. CLose to the decepticon base here." he pointed slighty 
to the right. "they may be a problem."
